## Executive Summary

This roadmap transforms Bessie from a functional forecasting agent into a **production-grade enterprise FP&A AI system** with three interconnected enhancements:

| Phase | Initiative | Priority | Estimated Effort |
|---|---|---|---|
| 1 | Security & Governance Guardrails | 🔴 Immediate | 2–3 weeks |
| 2 | RAG Knowledge Pipeline | 🟡 High | 4–6 weeks |
| 3 | QA Review Agent | 🟡 High | 3–4 weeks |

**Guiding principle across all phases:** AI explains and interprets — deterministic code calculates. Bessie should never be trusted to perform arithmetic; she should only reason about numbers computed by verified code.

